description:
This is a 29 minute workout called 'Strong in 30! FULL BODY dumbbell workout to strengthen and sculpt!' from the channel Cheryl Coulombe.
The workout falls under Strength/Weight workout.
It's suitable for Intermediate and Advanced fitness levels.
You'll need Weights and Weights for this workout.
The workout has a The Progression Quest and The Masterclass Workout vibe.
The technique difficulty is Intermediate.
The effort required is Moderate and Challenging.

Original workout description: Weight lifting for women at home! Join me for this 30 minute full body dumbbell workout. Strengthen and sculpt the total body, lifting weights at home. Low impact means no jumping or fast movements during this weight training workout. 

#homeworkout #dumbbellworkout  #strengthworkout 
____ 
Warm Up   

ONE
1. Sumo deadlift 55lb/25kg (my dumbbell weight for reference only) 
2. Bent arm side lateral raise 15lb/6.5kg
 
TWO
1. Goblet squat 55lb/25kg
2. Dumbbell pullover 30lb/14kg (bench or from floor)

THREE
1. Alternating cross body hammer curl 17.5lb/8kg
2. Skiers 17.5lb/8kg
3. Bird dog (bodyweight)

Cool down stretch 
____

✅ W O R K O U T  P R O G R A M
Complete three LIFT WITH CEE  full body workouts each week.
You can either:
- Repeat this video 3x/week for a 4-8 week training block (called a mesocycle)
- Pick a different video 3x/week from a 30 min or 40 min workout playlist
